# NOTE: This file has been automatically generated from a template file at 15_management-certificates.radtmpl.
#
# The file was generated with the following template values:
# - Management UI/API certificate (chain) file: MANAGEMENT_API_CERT
# - Management UI/API private key file for the certificate: MANAGEMENT_API_KEY
# - Management UI/API private key password if any: whatever
#
